        <updateDate>2005-09-21T15:50:55Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Teacher Loan Hurricane Relief Act - Authorizes the Secretary of Education to waive the consecutive service requirements of the student loan forgiveness program, under the Higher Education Act of 1965, for teachers whose employment is interrupted in schools in major disaster areas caused by Hurricane Katrina.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
